1
01:00:23,041 --> 01:00:25,583
[MICHELLE] Lucy, please!
Save yourself!

2
01:00:25,666 --> 01:00:28,458
[LUCY] That's not happening!
I'm gonna stick with you!

3
01:00:35,625 --> 01:00:40,583
♪

4
01:02:05,583 --> 01:02:08,791
So now we've
gotta fight that?

5
01:02:08,875 --> 01:02:10,583
A big octopus!

6
01:02:10,666 --> 01:02:12,958
[BYRO] Why do you
insist on defying us?

7
01:02:13,041 --> 01:02:17,250
You'll get out of our way
if you know what's good for you.

8
01:02:17,333 --> 01:02:19,208
[SUGARBOY] Don't get me
wrong, it's been real fun

9
01:02:19,291 --> 01:02:21,750
but we gotta close the
curtain on this here show.

10
01:02:21,833 --> 01:02:24,875
Aloha.
Time to go our separate ways.

11
01:02:24,958 --> 01:02:26,375
[NATSU] Happy.

12
01:02:26,458 --> 01:02:29,291
Do you think ridin' on that
thing would make me sick?

13
01:02:29,375 --> 01:02:31,125
Why would you ask
such a stupid question?

14
01:02:31,208 --> 01:02:32,875
It's clearly not a vehicle!

15
01:02:32,958 --> 01:02:34,083
[NATSU] Well,
anything that big is

16
01:02:34,166 --> 01:02:36,791
automatically a
vehicle in my eyes!

17
01:02:37,583 --> 01:02:40,000
Just lookin' at it is
makin' me nauseous!

18
01:02:40,083 --> 01:02:41,666
You're such a baby!

19
01:02:41,750 --> 01:02:45,333
[SUGARBOY] Uh-huh.
Let's get spicy!

20
01:02:48,208 --> 01:02:49,500
[NATSU] You want spicy?

21
01:02:49,583 --> 01:02:52,541
I'll give you
straight up blazin'!

22
01:02:52,625 --> 01:02:56,208
[NATSU] Fire Dragon Roar!

23
01:03:00,166 --> 01:03:03,458
Natsu's flames--
they vanished!

24
01:03:04,625 --> 01:03:05,916
Nice try, son.

25
01:03:06,000 --> 01:03:07,666
But you oughta know
that your great balls of fire

26
01:03:07,750 --> 01:03:09,416
ain't got nothin' on Lord Byro.

27
01:03:09,500 --> 01:03:12,083
[NATSU] How come nobody
bothered to tell me that?

28
01:03:13,291 --> 01:03:18,750
[NATSU] Fire Dragon Wing Attack!

29
01:03:25,458 --> 01:03:28,416
No!
It was absorbed!

30
01:03:28,500 --> 01:03:33,458
Now doggies! C'mon!
Crazy arms!

31
01:03:43,375 --> 01:03:45,291
[HAPPY] Sugarboy's
magic actually feeds

32
01:03:45,375 --> 01:03:47,708
off of his opponent's power.

33
01:03:47,791 --> 01:03:50,541
[BYRO] Eliminate them.
Quickly.

34
01:03:51,666 --> 01:03:54,125
[SUGARBOY] Gotcha covered,
big boss man.

35
01:03:59,833 --> 01:04:01,333
[NATSU] Hey octopus freak!

36
01:04:01,416 --> 01:04:03,750
Just where do you
think you're goin'?

37
01:04:03,833 --> 01:04:07,541
Lord Byro ain't got
the time to deal with you.

38
01:04:11,625 --> 01:04:13,708
[HAPPY] The Fury of Legion!

39
01:04:15,083 --> 01:04:17,458
[screams]

40
01:04:17,541 --> 01:04:20,541
[LUCY] I've got this!
Open Gate of the Ram!

41
01:04:20,625 --> 01:04:21,958
Aries!

42
01:04:22,041 --> 01:04:22,666
[doorbell sound]

43
01:04:22,750 --> 01:04:25,166
[ARIES] Oh, I'm sorry!

44
01:04:28,583 --> 01:04:30,458
I get so nervous
whenever you call me!

45
01:04:30,541 --> 01:04:32,250
I hope I did okay!

46
01:04:32,333 --> 01:04:35,250
Yeah, that was perfect timing!
Thank you!

47
01:04:35,333 --> 01:04:37,958
[MICHELLE] Wow! That
was a close one, huh?

48
01:04:38,041 --> 01:04:39,750
[MARY] I totes dunno
what your damage is

49
01:04:39,833 --> 01:04:42,291
but you don't know
when to give up.

50
01:04:42,708 --> 01:04:44,583
I'll show you.

51
01:04:45,250 --> 01:04:48,458
Open Gate of the
Golden Bull! Taurus!

52
01:04:48,541 --> 01:04:50,791
[doorbell sound]

53
01:04:50,875 --> 01:04:52,833
[TAURUS] Looks like you need
some help protecting a babe

54
01:04:52,916 --> 01:04:55,916
at the bottom of a
cliff, Miss Lucy!

55
01:04:56,000 --> 01:04:57,125
[TAURUS] Have I
told you lately that you

56
01:04:57,208 --> 01:04:59,500
have a really nice body?

57
01:04:59,583 --> 01:05:00,541
[LUCY] Ugh!

58
01:05:00,625 --> 01:05:01,416
I'd give you an
earful but we don't

59
01:05:01,500 --> 01:05:02,958
have time for that right now!

60
01:05:03,041 --> 01:05:06,500
Just hurry and
beat her up, okay?

61
01:05:06,583 --> 01:05:08,666
You can udderly
count on me!

62
01:05:08,750 --> 01:05:11,541
You're totes nuts if
you think a cow can beat me!

63
01:05:11,625 --> 01:05:13,208
As if!

64
01:05:17,250 --> 01:05:19,166
She's not controlling
him, is she?

65
01:05:19,250 --> 01:05:22,416
I knew it! Her magic power
can only control humans!

66
01:05:22,500 --> 01:05:25,416
It has no effect on
Celestial Spirits!

67
01:05:31,916 --> 01:05:34,333
Why'd you stop, Taurus?
What's wrong?

68
01:05:34,416 --> 01:05:37,125
[TAURUS] Whoa.
Holy cow.

69
01:05:37,750 --> 01:05:39,458
I know that you
really want me to fight her

70
01:05:39,541 --> 01:05:42,166
but she's got a nice body, too!

71
01:05:43,666 --> 01:05:44,666
Who cares?

72
01:05:44,750 --> 01:05:46,416
What's that got to
do with anything?

73
01:05:46,500 --> 01:05:48,958
I can't attack her because
I just wanna smooch her!

74
01:05:49,041 --> 01:05:50,291
Go away!

75
01:05:51,208 --> 01:05:53,166
Is it just me
or do all of your

76
01:05:53,250 --> 01:05:57,708
Celestial Spirits have
incredibly unique personalities?

77
01:05:57,791 --> 01:06:01,375
No kidding. That's an extremely
polite way of putting it.

78
01:06:01,458 --> 01:06:03,583
But at least they're consistent.

79
01:06:04,208 --> 01:06:06,333
What am I doing
wasting time like this?

80
01:06:06,416 --> 01:06:09,041
Scorpio!
You're up!

81
01:06:11,666 --> 01:06:14,958
Wicked! You just
leave this to me, Lucy.

82
01:06:15,041 --> 01:06:15,875
Aw, yeah!

83
01:06:15,958 --> 01:06:18,041
Yep, definitely unique.

84
01:06:25,625 --> 01:06:26,833
What do we do?

85
01:06:26,916 --> 01:06:28,125
She's so
fast I don't think

86
01:06:28,208 --> 01:06:30,125
there's much
we really can do!

87
01:06:38,250 --> 01:06:39,708
[PANTHERLILY]
We have to defeat her.

88
01:06:39,791 --> 01:06:42,041
Even though she's the
spitting image of Coco,

89
01:06:42,125 --> 01:06:45,125
she's not the same girl
we knew back in Edolas.

90
01:06:46,791 --> 01:06:50,125
I really should've known better.
Stand back, ladies.

91
01:06:57,791 --> 01:07:00,208
[BYRO] What is it, Kanaloa?

92
01:07:00,791 --> 01:07:02,958
You've found something,
haven't you?

93
01:07:03,041 --> 01:07:05,791
Yes.
I sense it, too.

94
01:07:08,791 --> 01:07:12,083
[BYRO] You're the one I sensed.
I must admit, you hold an

95
01:07:12,166 --> 01:07:14,833
impressive amount
of magic power.

96
01:07:14,916 --> 01:07:16,500
Y'don't say.

97
01:07:18,500 --> 01:07:20,416
I know who
you are, good sir,

98
01:07:20,500 --> 01:07:22,375
your reputation precedes you.

99
01:07:22,458 --> 01:07:24,041
The most powerful
wizard of the

100
01:07:24,125 --> 01:07:29,791
Fairy Tail guild's elite
S-Class. Gildarts Clive.

101
01:07:31,666 --> 01:07:34,000
Well, I dunno
who you are...

102
01:07:34,083 --> 01:07:35,375
But you must have a death wish

103
01:07:35,458 --> 01:07:37,958
if you're messin'
with Fairy Tail.

104
01:07:38,041 --> 01:07:41,125
[BYRO] I don't necessarily
have business with your guild.

105
01:07:41,208 --> 01:07:42,583
[GILDARTS] Is that so?

106
01:07:44,041 --> 01:07:46,458
Cool!

107
01:07:47,250 --> 01:07:49,916
I thought I told you
to quit following me.

108
01:07:50,000 --> 01:07:51,958
But this is my
big chance, y'know?

109
01:07:52,041 --> 01:07:55,250
This is the juiciest scoop in
the history of Sorcerer Weekly!

110
01:07:55,333 --> 01:07:56,916
"Twenty-four
Hours with Gildarts.

111
01:07:57,000 --> 01:07:58,541
A Journey into
Light and Shadows!"

112
01:07:58,625 --> 01:08:00,500
I can't believe that I just
started writing and

113
01:08:00,583 --> 01:08:04,375
now I'm about to witness one of
the coolest face-offs ever!

114
01:08:04,458 --> 01:08:05,750
[JASON] The last
showdown was awesome

115
01:08:05,833 --> 01:08:08,708
but this one's against
a freakin' octopus!

116
01:08:09,958 --> 01:08:11,041
I dunno which
one of you

117
01:08:11,125 --> 01:08:12,833
I should take down first.

118
01:08:12,916 --> 01:08:15,708
The octopus.
Or you.

119
01:08:15,791 --> 01:08:18,208
If you continue to
threaten me, Gildarts,

120
01:08:18,291 --> 01:08:21,291
I will be forced
to eliminate you.

121
01:08:33,041 --> 01:08:34,791
[GILDARTS] You say
you're gonna eliminate me

122
01:08:34,875 --> 01:08:37,333
but it looks like all you did
was get outta the way.

123
01:08:37,416 --> 01:08:39,708
[BYRO] No. I did
nothing of the sort;

124
01:08:39,791 --> 01:08:42,250
I merely neutralized your magic.

125
01:08:42,333 --> 01:08:44,958
[BYRO] More precisely...
I dispersed your attack

126
01:08:45,041 --> 01:08:46,583
and redirected
it around me.

127
01:08:46,666 --> 01:08:49,416
It was not a defensive maneuver.

128
01:08:51,791 --> 01:08:53,708
[JASON] And once it got around
him it came together again

129
01:08:53,791 --> 01:08:55,250
and hit the trees
right behind him!

130
01:08:55,333 --> 01:08:57,166
It broke 'em down into
hundreds of little blocks!

131
01:08:57,250 --> 01:08:58,041
Boom!

132
01:08:58,125 --> 01:08:59,583
That's some trick.

133
01:08:59,666 --> 01:09:00,791
It is, indeed.

134
01:09:00,875 --> 01:09:02,541
I'd show you more
but I don't have

135
01:09:02,625 --> 01:09:04,791
the time to waste
fighting you right now.

136
01:09:04,875 --> 01:09:08,208
My comrades and I have
an important task to complete.

137
01:09:08,291 --> 01:09:10,000
And what's that?

138
01:09:10,083 --> 01:09:14,166
Please attack me. It'll give
me reason to destroy you.

139
01:09:16,208 --> 01:09:17,375
[SCORPIO] Blam!

140
01:09:18,291 --> 01:09:20,541
Hurry Scorpio!
Shoot her again!

141
01:09:20,625 --> 01:09:23,041
You got it!
I'll hit her this time!

142
01:09:23,125 --> 01:09:24,708
Sand Spear!

143
01:09:25,416 --> 01:09:26,833
Don't try it!

144
01:09:29,833 --> 01:09:30,333
[SCORPIO] No!

145
01:09:30,416 --> 01:09:31,666
Lucy watch out!

146
01:09:37,250 --> 01:09:38,208
Michelle!

147
01:09:38,291 --> 01:09:41,041
Aw man! That
is totally my bad!

148
01:09:45,416 --> 01:09:47,291
[HAPPY] The more you
attack it, the more magic power

149
01:09:47,375 --> 01:09:49,000
it sucks up,
and the bigger it gets!

150
01:09:49,083 --> 01:09:51,125
What do you think we should do?

151
01:09:51,666 --> 01:09:53,250
There's only
one thing to do.

152
01:09:53,333 --> 01:09:56,208
I ain't losing to that blob!
I'm gonna burn it to a crisp!

153
01:09:56,291 --> 01:09:58,041
Don't do it, Natsu!

154
01:09:58,583 --> 01:10:02,333
[NATSU] Fire Dragon Iron Fist!

155
01:10:04,166 --> 01:10:06,666
You really shoulda listened
to your blue suede friend.

156
01:10:11,000 --> 01:10:12,583
It turned into fire!

157
01:10:12,666 --> 01:10:15,625
Uh-huh, my doggies don't just
absorb magic attacks.

158
01:10:15,708 --> 01:10:17,250
They take em in and
make them their own,

159
01:10:17,333 --> 01:10:19,833
like a real good cover tune.

160
01:10:24,833 --> 01:10:26,333
Oh no!

161
01:10:28,291 --> 01:10:32,708
[Natsu cries out
as he is struck]

162
01:10:35,583 --> 01:10:37,291
I can't believe
this is happening!

163
01:10:37,375 --> 01:10:38,750
He's losing to fire!

164
01:10:38,833 --> 01:10:41,500
You surprised? You shouldn't
be 'cause the more mojo

165
01:10:41,583 --> 01:10:45,041
that goo absorbs the stronger
and stronger that it becomes.

166
01:10:45,125 --> 01:10:48,666
So tell me, do ya get it now,
ya pretty blue kitty cat?

167
01:10:48,750 --> 01:10:50,875
Don't give me a weird
nickname, freakazoid!

168
01:10:50,958 --> 01:10:52,625
Run! Natsu!

169
01:10:52,708 --> 01:10:55,791
Yeah. I wish
I could 'lil buddy.

170
01:10:57,083 --> 01:11:03,125
But I don't think this slimy
fire--is gonna let me do that!

171
01:11:03,208 --> 01:11:05,750
Yeah! How you
like that, hot boy?

172
01:11:05,833 --> 01:11:08,708
The fire's burnin'!

173
01:11:08,791 --> 01:11:12,458
Natsu's the name of
my hound dog's latest flame!

174
01:11:12,541 --> 01:11:14,333
Woo hoo!!

175
01:11:14,958 --> 01:11:15,750
[Natsu cries out]

176
01:11:15,833 --> 01:11:17,458
Now I'm all shook up!

177
01:11:17,541 --> 01:11:19,625
Yeah!
C'mon, baby!

178
01:11:19,708 --> 01:11:21,083
Let's grow!

179
01:11:21,166 --> 01:11:22,958
[Natsu cries out]

180
01:11:28,791 --> 01:11:31,041
You're stronger than
I thought you were.

181
01:11:32,166 --> 01:11:33,916
Same goes for you.

182
01:11:36,750 --> 01:11:38,208
Yeah, crush him!

183
01:11:42,375 --> 01:11:44,291
[JASON] He neutralized
your attack again!

184
01:11:44,375 --> 01:11:46,333
Man, this dude
is freakin' awesome!

185
01:11:46,416 --> 01:11:48,500
So cool!

186
01:11:48,583 --> 01:11:50,666
Stand down.
I won't ask again.

187
01:11:50,750 --> 01:11:54,083
Go ahead and make me.
That is, if you think you can.

188
01:11:54,166 --> 01:11:56,166
[BYRO] Very well then.
I'm afraid you

189
01:11:56,250 --> 01:11:58,416
leave me with
no other choice.

190
01:12:12,000 --> 01:12:16,166
[battle sounds]

191
01:12:21,208 --> 01:12:24,541
You're really starting to
get on my last nerve, buddy.

192
01:12:24,625 --> 01:12:27,125
[BYRO] I feel the
same about you.

193
01:12:27,208 --> 01:12:30,583
Tell me, what exactly
is your goal here?

194
01:12:30,666 --> 01:12:31,958
Well?

195
01:12:32,041 --> 01:12:34,375
You wanna tell me why
you're destroying our guild?

196
01:12:34,458 --> 01:12:36,583
We're "destroying your guild"?

197
01:12:36,666 --> 01:12:38,541
What nonsense.

198
01:12:39,625 --> 01:12:42,041
[LUCY] Unlike Kain's
Witching Hour Curse magic,

199
01:12:42,125 --> 01:12:45,250
hers doesn't require a
strand of the target's hair.

200
01:12:45,750 --> 01:12:47,916
[LUCY THINKS] She can only
control one person at a time and

201
01:12:48,000 --> 01:12:50,666
they have to be within a
certain distance from her.

202
01:12:50,750 --> 01:12:53,708
So, I'm safe as long as I
stay away but that's easier

203
01:12:53,791 --> 01:12:56,791
said than done
in a situation like this.

204
01:13:00,250 --> 01:13:03,333
[COCO] Would you just spill it?
I'm running outta patience!

205
01:13:05,041 --> 01:13:07,208
[COCO]
Tell me where I can find her!

206
01:13:07,291 --> 01:13:09,875
Stop Lily! What do
you think you're doing?

207
01:13:13,666 --> 01:13:15,458
Let me handle this!

208
01:13:16,833 --> 01:13:19,791
Sky Dragon Roar!

209
01:13:24,750 --> 01:13:25,916
No! I missed!

210
01:13:26,000 --> 01:13:28,583
She can even outrun
your sky magic?

211
01:13:30,208 --> 01:13:31,541
[SUGARBOY] I'll be
taking any requests you

212
01:13:31,625 --> 01:13:34,500
got to finish you off, hot boy.
Go on and say the word.

213
01:13:36,333 --> 01:13:37,750
Natsu!

214
01:13:38,333 --> 01:13:41,833
Happy... Fly me
outta here quick.

215
01:13:42,583 --> 01:13:43,875
What are you
planing to do?

216
01:13:43,958 --> 01:13:46,250
What's it matter?
Just do it, okay?

217
01:13:47,375 --> 01:13:48,708
Aye, sir!

218
01:13:52,208 --> 01:13:53,916
There ain't no gettin'
away from me!

219
01:13:54,000 --> 01:13:56,166
My hound dog's gonna get ya!

220
01:13:56,666 --> 01:13:57,958
Listen, Happy.

221
01:13:58,041 --> 01:13:59,833
I want you to fly
over that slime

222
01:13:59,916 --> 01:14:01,166
and drop me into
the middle of it.

223
01:14:01,250 --> 01:14:04,541
Are you out of your mind?
I can't do that to you!

224
01:14:04,625 --> 01:14:07,041
That thing'll drain all
your magic power!

225
01:14:07,125 --> 01:14:08,541
Just trust me on this!

226
01:14:08,625 --> 01:14:10,125
[HAPPY] Aye!

227
01:14:12,708 --> 01:14:15,000
[HAPPY] Here ya go!

228
01:14:15,083 --> 01:14:18,291
I've had enough of
your stubborn sliminess!

229
01:14:20,541 --> 01:14:22,458
Wow, talk about
a dumb move, hot boy!

230
01:14:22,541 --> 01:14:25,458
Ya know wise men
say only fools rush in!

231
01:14:26,291 --> 01:14:27,750
That's spicy!

232
01:14:28,541 --> 01:14:31,333
[HAPPY] I wish I knew
what you were trying to do.

233
01:14:31,791 --> 01:14:33,500
[HAPPY] That's it!

234
01:14:33,583 --> 01:14:38,833
[Natsu powering  up]

235
01:14:39,416 --> 01:14:41,875
Now that's my little hound dog!
Eat up!

236
01:14:41,958 --> 01:14:44,833
You know you wanna gobble
down of his tasty mojo!

237
01:14:44,916 --> 01:14:48,458
Yeah!
Yummy!

238
01:14:50,875 --> 01:14:53,166
We got double trouble!

239
01:14:59,791 --> 01:15:01,458
No! My doggies ate so much

240
01:15:01,541 --> 01:15:04,208
of his witchcraft
they went kablooey!

241
01:15:07,375 --> 01:15:08,708
[SUGARBOY] Get back, jack!

242
01:15:21,291 --> 01:15:23,958
Uh-oh! Looks
like you're stuck!

243
01:15:24,791 --> 01:15:26,250
Let go my hand, man!

244
01:15:26,333 --> 01:15:29,375
I'm tellin' ya, if it absorbs
any more of your crazy mojo,

245
01:15:29,458 --> 01:15:31,458
it's gonna blow
both of us sky high!

246
01:15:31,541 --> 01:15:32,916
[NATSU] Ya Prob'ly
shoulda thought about that

247
01:15:33,000 --> 01:15:36,541
before you attacked me! If
