[GILDARTS] When
somebody attacks my guild

270
01:16:58,458 --> 01:17:00,791
it's definitely my business!

271
01:17:02,375 --> 01:17:03,916
Honestly, I'm not
too worried because

272
01:17:04,000 --> 01:17:06,125
Fairy Tail won't
be defeated easily.

273
01:17:07,041 --> 01:17:10,250
