274
01:17:10,333 --> 01:17:13,083
I'm not takin'
any chances.

275
01:17:14,666 --> 01:17:17,708
Because one of the guild's
members is my daughter.

276
01:17:18,041 --> 01:17:19,666
[BYRO] Oh?
Don't worry.

277
01:17:19,750 --> 01:17:21,875
We don't mean any
harm to your daughter.

278
01:17:21,958 --> 01:17:24,500
We want Lucy Heartfilia.

279
01:17:25,083 --> 01:17:26,791
[GILDARTS] What do
you want with her?

280
01:17:31,916 --> 01:17:35,708
[BYRO] My, suddenly there's a
serious look in your eyes.

281
01:17:35,791 --> 01:17:38,958
[BYRO] This is very
serious to us as well.

282
01:17:39,041 --> 01:17:41,500
We have been ordered
to complete a task.

283
01:17:41,583 --> 01:17:44,833
Given to us by the
Archbishop of Zentopia.

284
01:17:44,916 --> 01:17:47,250
This is "Holy war."

285
01:17:47,333 --> 01:17:49,291
 "Holy war"?

286
01:17:49,375 --> 01:17:54,250
Yes. This war
will change everything.

287
01:17:54,333 --> 01:17:57,708
There is no stopping us.

288
01:17:59,833 --> 01:18:01,125
Run, kid!

289
01:18:02,166 --> 01:18:04,000
