do what I say right now

290
01:18:04,083 --> 01:18:05,916
unless you wanna
die in the field!

291
01:18:06,000 --> 01:18:07,333
So run!

292
01:18:11,625 --> 01:18:12,916
Well?

293
01:18:21,333 --> 01:18:23,375
I totes found ya!

294
01:18:25,708 --> 01:18:28,375
Geez. That took longer
than I thought it would.

295
01:18:28,458 --> 01:18:30,250
I guess if we had known
what you actually look like,

296
01:18:30,333 --> 01:18:32,708
it would have been totes easy.

297
01:18:33,375 --> 01:18:35,250
Wake up!
Michelle!

298
01:18:35,333 --> 01:18:37,416
I need help!

299
01:18:39,208 --> 01:18:40,958
Got ya now!

300
01:18:41,041 --> 01:18:44,208
What're you waitin' for?
Seriously, like, get over here!

301
01:19:00,375 --> 01:19:03,708
Tell me, why are you
and your pals after Lucy?

302
01:19:04,708 --> 01:19:06,916
Strictly speaking,
we don't have any

303
01:19:07,000 --> 01:19:09,541
business with the girl herself.

304
01:19:09,625 --> 01:19:12,833
She has something
that we want.

305
01:19:18,333 --> 01:19:20,250
[NATSU] Just lemme
hit you dang it!

306
01:19:20,333 --> 01:19:21,541
C'mere!

307
01:19:21,625 --> 01:19:22,666
That's enough.

308
01:19:22,750 --> 01:19:23,916
This has been fun
but you need to

309
