get your hand outta mine.

310
01:19:25,208 --> 01:19:26,708
I don't mean to
be cruel or anything

311
01:19:26,791 --> 01:19:28,541
but this is kinda weird.

312
01:19:28,625 --> 01:19:29,791
Ya see I just
don't wanna be

313
01:19:29,875 --> 01:19:31,583
