314
01:19:31,666 --> 01:19:33,708
I ain't holdin' your hand
'cause I want to, bonehead!

315
01:19:33,791 --> 01:19:35,583
If you're gonna be a
hard headed woman about this

316
01:19:35,666 --> 01:19:38,291
