snot outta you til you let go!

317
01:19:40,583 --> 01:19:41,833
[SUGARBOY] Ya like that?

318
01:19:45,375 --> 01:19:47,958
That should do the trick.
Now, flip, flop, and fly.

319
01:19:48,458 --> 01:19:50,708
[GRAY] Ice Cannon!

320
01:19:53,833 --> 01:19:55,791
Geez, Gray!
What's the big idea?

321
01:19:55,875 --> 01:19:57,750
You nearly broke my arm, y'know!

322
01:19:57,833 --> 01:20:00,458
[GRAY] I saved your
hide so quit complainin'.

323
01:20:00,541 --> 01:20:03,458
You should be
thankin' me, flamebrain.

324
01:20:05,375 --> 01:20:07,250
No, it can't be.

325
01:20:12,750 --> 01:20:17,750
[SUGARBOY] I'll call you
"ice boy". That's spicy!

326
01:20:17,833 --> 01:20:19,958
[GRAY] I'm not answerin'
to some weird nickname!

327
01:20:20,041 --> 01:20:22,333
What the heck are
you doing here anyway?

328
01:20:22,416 --> 01:20:23,791
It's not what you think, Gray!

329
01:20:23,875 --> 01:20:26,708
This isn't the guy we met;
this is Earth Land Sugarboy!

330
01:20:26,791 --> 01:20:27,958
[GRAY] Huh?

331
